        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息連續兩日全線跌　隔夜拆息急跌至1.19厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15471243&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元銀行同業拆息連續兩日全線下跌，當中，短息跌幅較為明顯。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜拆息由上星期五的近3.1厘，急跌至1.19厘，跌幅近1.9厘，創近兩星期新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">1星期及兩星期均跌穿2厘，單日跌幅近1厘或以上，兩星期拆息是自8月中旬以來首次失守2厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">與供樓相關的1個月拆息失守3厘，跌至2.93厘，跌近25個點子，連跌兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">6個月及12個月拆息微跌，仍守在3厘以上。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15471243-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e9%80%a3%e7%ba%8c%e5%85%a9%e6%97%a5%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e8%b7%8c%e3%80%80%e9%9a%94%e5%a4%9c%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e6%80%a5%e8%b7%8c%e8%87%b31-19%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/bplib_20230707-125251_20230707_FI_source-licensed_HKD_shutterstock_fb_source-licensed_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 08:30:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "雅居樂11月預售額按年跌46.67% 今年累計亦降45.22%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雅居樂(03383)公布，今年11月公司旗下及由公司管理並以「雅居樂」品牌銷售的房地產項目，預售金額約6.4億元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：雅居樂官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230727_FI_source-web_AGILE-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：雅居樂官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230727_FI_source-web_AGILE-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：雅居樂官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述數字較去年同期的12億元跌46.67%；涉及樓面7萬平方米，均價每平方米9083元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年以來累計預售額則為80.8億元，較去年同期的147.5億元減少45.22%；涉及樓面88.6萬平方米，均價每平方米9113元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15478990-%e9%9b%85%e5%b1%85%e6%a8%8211%e6%9c%88%e9%a0%90%e5%94%ae%e9%a1%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c46-67-%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e4%ba%a6%e9%99%8d45-22",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_FI_source-web_03383-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 08:25:38",
